ullah said, \u201cGreed.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 595\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33999,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/02\/16\/hasan-ilm-two-types\/","url_meta":{"origin":35122,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on \u2018Ilm: Knowledge is two types, beneficial or hypocritical","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Hisham reported: Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cKnowledge is two types: Knowledge in the heart is that which benefits. Knowledge on the tongue will be an indictment against the son of Adam.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 376 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0647\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0627\u0645 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31825,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/08\/shabi-whims-whisk-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":35122,"position":2},"title":"Sha\u2019bi on Whims: Lowly desires whisk their companions to Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Shubrumah reported: Al-Sha\u2019bi, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, whims are only named as such because they whisk their companions away to the Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 398 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0634\u064f\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064f\u0645\u0651\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0649 \u0644\u0650\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0648\u0650\u064a \u0628\u0650\u0635\u064e\u0627\u062d\u0650\u0628\u0650\u0647\u0650 \u064a\u0639\u0646\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0627\u0631 398 \u0633\u0646\u0646\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38271,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/28\/allahu-alam\/","url_meta":{"origin":35122,"position":3},"title":"Ali on Ignorance: When to say Allah knows best","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 28, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Razin Abi al-Nu\u2019man reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhen you are asked about what you do not know, then flee.\u201d It was said, \u201cO leader of the faithful, how does one flee?\u201d Ali said, \u201cThat you say: Allah knows best.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35134,"url":"http